Binomial(10, 0.3)
P(x) = ((10) nCr (x))(0.3)^x(0.7)^(10-x)
P(4) = (10 nCr 4) * (0.3)^4*(0.7)^6=0.200
Hypergometeric(500 000, 500, 10)
P(x) = (500 nCr x)(450000 nCr 10-x)/(500000 nCr 10)
P(X >= 1) = 1 - P(0) = 1 - [(500 nCr 0)(450000 nCr 10)/(500000 nCr 10)]= 0.651
